snippet.title: NIGHTCORE - huken x murkish - WASTED [Juice Wrld x Lil Uzi Vert]
snippet.description:
Figured it was about time we made an official version of the nightcore remix. It's mostly the same as the version that's been out for a while, just higher quality and with a few tweaks to sound better at a higher pitch from the original. 

Shoutout to Chair for the original idea to speed the track up

huken: https://soundcloud.com/hvken
murkish: https://soundcloud.com/murkish
